122
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,160
Xiaoxiao.

123
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,279
Xiaoxiao.

124
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,720
Xiaoxiao.

125
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,839
Xiaoxiao.

126
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:59,519
Xiaoxiao, where are you?

127
00:08:57,120 --> 00:09:00,799
(Xiaoxiao, where did you go?)

128
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:03,639
(You didn't just leave, right?)

129
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,559
(Without you here,)

130
00:09:06,919 --> 00:09:08,759
(I can't even
stay with Her Highness alone.)

131
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,039
What's wrong? You seem lost.

132
00:09:21,799 --> 00:09:22,480
It's nothing.

133
00:09:23,159 --> 00:09:24,200
What can I do for you?

134
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,120
Let's take a bath.

135
00:09:27,519 --> 00:09:29,399
Rain check.

136
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:31,720
Let's get warmed up.

137
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:34,200
The martial arts meeting is coming up.

138
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,759
We must discuss the details.

139
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,519
Does it have to be today?

140
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:43,200
What's wrong? Why are you so hesitant?

141
00:09:44,399 --> 00:09:45,440
You're tired of this place?

142
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,919
Let's go to my mansion.

143
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,679
Okay.

144
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,879
Where is Chu Xiaoran?

145
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,799
Young Master Chu?

146
00:10:07,559 --> 00:10:09,120
He's been at the duke's mansion for days

147
00:10:09,279 --> 00:10:10,200
and hasn't come back.

148
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:12,480
Forget it. I should get rid of someone

149
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,279
I can't control.

150
00:10:13,399 --> 00:10:15,559
Understood. I will have him killed now.

151
00:10:15,919 --> 00:10:16,559
Come back.

152
00:10:19,399 --> 00:10:21,159
What's going on with you?

153
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:22,679
Are you influenced by Chu Xiaoran?

154
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:23,519
No.

155
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:25,360
I just feel that he will slow you down

156
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,919
when you draw your sword

157
00:10:26,919 --> 00:10:28,320
and affect your major decisions.

158
00:10:31,679 --> 00:10:32,919
